list.name: Changes
list.comment:
Updated the Page to be much more production quality.
Site isn't a complete eyesore to look at and functions properly with added features like cookie management, usernames, and a username changer, as well as a dynamic welcoming system that welcomes the user differently whether they have visited the site or they are new.

task.summary:
Created Basic HTML page with basic CSS to demonstrate the UI for later.
Features two commands to communicate with an un-commited websocket version that allows the users to run '/history' to get previously sent messages, and '/clear' to clear the history and local page of any messages sent.
